<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="sl">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Trgovina | Lasersko graviranje Slovenija | JDSF Graviranje</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Premium trgovina za lasersko graviranje v Sloveniji: personalizirana darila, gravura na les in kovino ter unikatna darila po meri." />
    <meta property="og:title" content="Trgovina | JDSF Graviranje" />
    <meta property="og:description" content="Personalizirana darila in lasersko graviranje po meri: les, kovina in darila za posebne priložnosti." />
    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://girodayzzzz.github.io/JDSF-Engraving/shop.html" />
    <meta property="og:image" content="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1512909006721-3d6018887383?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1400&q=80" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css" />
  </head>
  <body class="shop-page">
    <header class="site-header" id="siteHeader"><div class="container nav-wrap"><a class="logo" href="index.html">JDSF</a><button class="nav-toggle" id="navToggle" aria-label="Preklopi navigacijo">☰</button><nav class="nav" id="navMenu"><a href="index.html">Domov</a><a href="shop.html" class="active">Trgovina</a><a href="about.html">O nas</a><a href="contact.html">Kontakt</a><a class="btn btn-primary btn-nav" href="contact.html">Pošlji povpraševanje</a></nav></div></header>

    <main class="shop-shell">
      <section class="shop-hero container">
        <p class="eyebrow">Trgovina</p>
        <h1>Trgovina</h1>
        <p class="shop-lead">Personalizirana laserska gravura po meri</p>
      </section>

      <section class="container shop-filters sticky-panel">
        <div class="filter-group" id="categoryFilters"></div>
        <input id="searchInput" type="search" placeholder="Išči po imenu izdelka..." aria-label="Išči izdelek" />
        <select id="sortSelect" aria-label="Razvrsti izdelke">
          <option value="">Razvrsti po</option>
          <option value="asc">Cena: najnižja</option>
          <option value="desc">Cena: najvišja</option>
        </select>
      </section>

      <section class="container">
        <div class="shop-grid" id="productGrid"></div>
        <p id="emptyState" class="empty-state" hidden>Za izbrane filtre trenutno ni izdelkov.</p>
      </section>
    </main>

    <div class="modal-backdrop" id="productModal" aria-hidden="true">
      <article class="shop-modal" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="modalTitle">
        <button id="closeModal" class="modal-close" type="button" aria-label="Zapri">✕</button>
        <img id="modalImage" src="" alt="" />
        <div>
          <p class="modal-category" id="modalCategory"></p>
          <h2 id="modalTitle"></h2>
          <p id="modalDescription"></p>
          <p class="modal-price" id="modalPrice"></p>
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="contact.html">Pošlji povpraševanje</a>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>

    <footer class="site-footer"><div class="container footer-grid"><div><a class="logo" href="index.html">JDSF</a><p>Unikatne laserske gravure po meri za darila, podjetja in posebne priložnosti.</p></div><div><h4>Hitre povezave</h4><ul><li><a href="index.html">Domov</a></li><li><a href="shop.html">Trgovina</a></li><li><a href="about.html">O nas</a></li><li><a href="contact.html">Kontakt</a></li></ul></div><div><h4>Kontakt</h4><p>E-pošta: <a href="mailto:hello@jdsfengraving.com">hello@jdsfengraving.com</a></p></div></div></footer>

    <script src="script.js"></script>
    <script src="js/products-loader.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
